author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what happens when manifesting tinfoil hat theories goes wrong. Today was supposed to be a day where a trailer for GTA could have dropped, in fact today was a day for Rockstar to just troll the community for a good laugh. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: It's A Very Sad Day For The GTA Community...
